__TOC__


The following list contains a list of translatable templates in Launchpad along with information about upstream message sharing.

The aim is to use it to coordinate the work of enabling the usage of upstream imports sharing in all supported templates, as per the UbuntuSpec:community-o-launchpad-translations-upstream-imports-presentation-and-plans blueprint for Oneiric.

In order to do this, we're setting up a community initiative to complete the '''Has upstream project''' and '''Has upstream link''' columns in the table.

For every source package, the next step is to <nowiki>[[Enable|enable upstream imports]]</nowiki>.
